sentences.english: Other songbirds, such as wrens, have hundreds of songs.

sentences.english: It says here that male blue fairy wrens have testicles that can weigh up to 25% of their body mass.

sentences.english: American wren that inhabits tall reed beds.
sentences.chinese: 栖息在高杆芦苇畦地的美洲鹪鹩。

sentences.english: And when that wren moves, it also abandons its mate.
sentences.chinese: 当鹪鹩换新住所时，也放弃它的伴侣。

sentences.english: Who'll bear the pall? "We, " said the Wren.
sentences.chinese: 谁来扶棺？是我们，鹪鹩说。
